[6.397417, "o", "$ claude_run List the available skills. Show just their names and one-line descriptions. Be brief.\r\n"]
[13.00725, "o", "\r\n\r\nHere are the available skills:\r\n\r\n| Skill | Description |\r\n|-------|-------------|\r\n| **update-config** | Configure Claude Code settings, hooks, permissions, and env vars |\r\n| **keybindings-help** | Customize keyboard shortcuts and keybindings |\r\n| **simplify** | Review changed code for reuse, quality, and efficiency |\r\n| **loop** | Run a prompt or slash command on a recurring interval |\r\n| **claude-api** | Build apps with the Claude API or Anthropic SDK |\r\n| **handoff** | Review changes made by another agent or session |\r\n| **helix** | HELIX test-first workflow with authority-ordered planning and Beads execution |\r\n| **helix-alignment-review** | Top-down reconciliation review of a HELIX project |\r\n| **review** | Critical review for errors, omissions, and principle compliance |"]
